imdb.plot outline: Jay's Jungle is a pre-school series that follows the adventures of Jay the lighthouse keeper. Jay lives on a J-shaped island, inside a lighthouse called C-Mor. Everyday, the wise C-Mor shines his magical light across the world searching for thoughts and questions to explore.
imdb.title: Jay's Jungle
plot: _Jay's Jungle_ (qv) is a pre-school series that follows the adventures of Jay the lighthouse keeper. Jay lives on a J-shaped island, inside a lighthouse called C-Mor. Everyday, the wise C-Mor shines his magical light across the world searching for thoughts and questions to explore.
